sql_prompt: average time resolve high severity vulnerability product comparing last quarter quarter previous year

sql_prompt: find top 5 goal scorer 2022 uefa champion league group stage including team name
sql: SELECT p.player_name, t.team_name, SUM(m.goals_home + m.goals_away) AS total_goals FROM ucl_players p JOIN (SELECT home_team_id AS team_id, SUM(goals_home) AS goals FROM ucl_matches GROUP BY home_team_id UNION ALL SELECT away_team_id, SUM(goals_away) FROM ucl_matches GROUP BY away_team_id) t ON p.team_id = t.team_id JOIN ucl_matches m ON p.team_id IN (m.home_team_id, m.away_team_id) WHERE m.match_id IN (SELECT match_id FROM ucl_matches WHERE (home_team_id = p.team_id OR away_team_id = p.team_id) AND match_id <= 6) GROUP BY p.player_id, t.team_name ORDER BY total_goals DESC LIMIT 5;

sql_prompt: percentage change rural poverty rate central america 20182020

sql_prompt: percentage patient followup appointment within 60 day initial appointment grouped physician saw type appointment
sql: SELECT Physician, AppointmentType, (SUM(FollowUpAppointments) / SUM(TotalAppointments)) * 100.0 FROM (SELECT Physician, AppointmentType, COUNT(*) AS TotalAppointments, SUM(CASE WHEN DATEDIFF(day, Appointments.Date, FollowUpAppointments.Date) <= 60 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS FollowUpAppointments FROM Appointments LEFT JOIN Appointments AS FollowUpAppointments ON Appointments.PatientID = FollowUpAppointments.PatientID WHERE FollowUpAppointments.Date IS NOT NULL GROUP BY Physician, AppointmentType) AS Subquery GROUP BY Physician, AppointmentType;

sql_prompt: system scanned last month maximum cve score

sql_prompt: many marine protected area exist indian ocean 2022
sql: SELECT num_areas FROM protected_areas WHERE ocean = 'Indian Ocean' AND year = 2022;

sql_prompt: maximum number simultaneous login attempt allowed corporate security policy
sql: SELECT MAX(max_simultaneous_logins) FROM security_policies WHERE policy_name = 'corporate';

sql_prompt: total number highseverity vulnerability software vendor last 6 month
sql: SELECT vendor, COUNT(*) FROM vulnerabilities WHERE severity >= 7 AND date >= '2022-01-01' GROUP BY vendor;

sql_prompt: calculate average claim amount policyholder living tx
sql: SELECT AVG(Claims.Amount) FROM Policyholders JOIN Claims ON Policyholders.PolicyholderID = Claims.PolicyholderID WHERE Policyholders.State = 'TX';

sql_prompt: name farmer adopted precision agriculture technique ruraldevelopment schema
sql: SELECT name FROM rural_development.farmers WHERE technique = 'Precision Agriculture';

sql_prompt: total number point scored la lakers 2020 nba season
sql: SELECT SUM(points) FROM team_points WHERE team = 'LA Lakers' AND sport = 'NBA' AND season = '2020';

sql_prompt: average rating hotel u virtual tour
sql: SELECT AVG(rating) FROM hotels WHERE country = 'USA' AND virtual_tour = true;

sql_prompt: spacecraft model used mission jupiter
sql: SELECT Spacecraft.Name FROM Spacecraft INNER JOIN SpacecraftMissions ON Spacecraft.SpacecraftID = SpacecraftMissions.SpacecraftID WHERE SpacecraftMissions.Destination = 'Jupiter';

sql_prompt: average time resolution high severity incident energy sector
sql: SELECT AVG(incident_resolution_time) FROM incidents WHERE incident_severity = 'High' AND incident_sector = 'Energy';

sql_prompt: list underwriting department ontario quebec count
sql: SELECT department, COUNT(*) FROM underwriting WHERE province IN ('ON', 'QC') GROUP BY department;

sql_prompt: minimum maximum age policyholder policy premium 1500 5000
sql: SELECT MIN(Age), MAX(Age) FROM Policyholders WHERE Premium BETWEEN 1500 AND 5000;

sql_prompt: community development initiative implemented india rural area 2015 2017 combined budget
sql: SELECT initiative, SUM(budget) FROM community_initiatives WHERE country = 'India' AND start_year BETWEEN 2015 AND 2017 AND end_year BETWEEN 2015 AND 2017 GROUP BY initiative;

sql_prompt: total number covid19 case oceania 2021
sql: SELECT SUM(cases) FROM covid WHERE region = 'Oceania' AND year = 2021;

sql_prompt: many employee hired q1 2022 underrepresented community
sql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Hiring WHERE QUARTER(HireDate) = 1 AND YEAR(HireDate) = 2022 AND Community IN ('LatinX', 'African American', 'LGBTQ+', 'Women in STEM');

sql_prompt: difference number ai project u number ai project eu
sql: SELECT COUNT(*) - (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM ai_projects.projects WHERE location = 'EU') as diff FROM ai_projects.projects WHERE location = 'USA';

sql_prompt: many local business madrid offer virtual experience
sql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM local_businesses WHERE city = 'Madrid' AND virtual_experience = true;

sql_prompt: list sustainable tourism initiative canada respective number participant
sql: SELECT initiatives.name, COUNT(participants.participant_id) FROM initiatives INNER JOIN participants ON initiatives.initiative_id = participants.initiative_id WHERE country = 'Canada' GROUP BY initiatives.name;

sql_prompt: percentage hotel adopting ai chatbots berlin
sql: SELECT 100.0 * SUM(ai_chatbot) / COUNT(*) FROM Adoption WHERE city = 'Berlin';

sql_prompt: list unique port country oil spill occurred last 5 year
sql: SELECT DISTINCT port, country FROM oil_spills WHERE date >= DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE, INTERVAL 5 YEAR);

sql_prompt: maximum donation amount given year 2022
sql: SELECT MAX(donation_amount) FROM donations WHERE YEAR(donation_date) = 2022;

sql_prompt: minimum donation amount donation table month 2021
sql: SELECT DATE_FORMAT(DonationDate, '%Y-%m') AS Month, MIN(DonationAmount) FROM Donations WHERE YEAR(DonationDate) = 2021 GROUP BY Month;

sql_prompt: identify number marine protected area arctic region
sql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM marine_protected_areas WHERE region = 'Arctic';

sql_prompt: average mass spacecraft manufactured galactic innovation
sql: SELECT AVG(mass) FROM Spacecrafts WHERE manufacturer = 'Galactic Innovations';

sql_prompt: recent launch date satellite manufactured indian space research organisation isro
sql: SELECT MAX(launch_date) FROM Satellite WHERE manufacturer_id = (SELECT id FROM Manufacturer WHERE name = 'Indian Space Research Organisation');

sql_prompt: number reported infectious disease case african country past year
sql: SELECT country, COUNT(*) FROM infectious_diseases WHERE country IN ('Nigeria', 'Egypt', 'South Africa') AND date >= DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE, INTERVAL 1 YEAR) GROUP BY country;

sql_prompt: total number digital divide initiative asia
sql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM digital_divide_initiatives WHERE region = 'Asia';

sql_prompt: list top 3 popular online travel agency canada booking
sql: SELECT ota_name, bookings FROM otas WHERE country = 'Canada' ORDER BY bookings DESC LIMIT 3;

sql_prompt: market share hotel chain c south america
sql: SELECT market_share * 100 FROM market_share_2 WHERE hotel_chain = 'Hotel Chain C';

sql_prompt: total revenue hotel america schema february
sql: SELECT hotel_name, SUM(revenue) FROM americas.hotel_revenue WHERE date_trunc('month', date) = '2023-02-01'::DATE GROUP BY hotel_name;

sql_prompt: average number test performed per day laboratory state texas
sql: SELECT AVG(tests_per_day) FROM laboratories WHERE state = 'Texas';

sql_prompt: whats average budget accessible technology project africa
sql: SELECT AVG(Budget) FROM Accessible_Tech_Projects WHERE Location = 'Africa';

sql_prompt: average rating ecofriendly hotel spain
sql: SELECT AVG(rating) FROM eco_hotels WHERE country = 'Spain';

sql_prompt: total revenue generated sustainable accommodation region
sql: SELECT region, SUM(price) as total_revenue FROM accommodation WHERE sustainable = 1 GROUP BY region;

sql_prompt: total revenue generated cultural heritage site tokyo
sql: SELECT SUM(revenue) FROM cultural_sites WHERE city = 'Tokyo';

sql_prompt: average rating hotel united state offer aipowered service
sql: SELECT AVG(rating) FROM hotels WHERE ai_services = true AND country = 'USA';

sql_prompt: maximum population marine specie atlantic ocean
sql: SELECT MAX(population) FROM marine_species WHERE location = 'Atlantic';

sql_prompt: many community development initiative completed brazil 2015 2019
sql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM community_development_initiatives WHERE country = 'Brazil' AND completion_year BETWEEN 2015 AND 2019;

sql_prompt: many rural infrastructure project completed 2020
sql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM rural_infrastructure WHERE YEAR(end_date) = 2020;

sql_prompt: difference average salary employee identify male female
sql: SELECT AVG(Employees.Salary) - (SELECT AVG(Employees.Salary) FROM Employees WHERE Gender = 'Male') AS Difference FROM Employees WHERE Gender = 'Female';

sql_prompt: many tennis match played grass court tennistournaments table
sql: SELECT SUM(matches) FROM tennis_tournaments WHERE court = 'Grass';

sql_prompt: total number fan attended football match manchester united year 2020
sql: SELECT SUM(fans_attended) FROM matches WHERE team = 'Manchester United' AND year = 2020;

sql_prompt: maximum number virtual tour engaged single day hotel new york city usa
sql: SELECT MAX(engagement_count) FROM virtual_tours vt INNER JOIN hotels h ON vt.hotel_id = h.id WHERE h.city = 'New York City' AND h.country = 'USA';

sql_prompt: calculate total biomass marine specie oceanmappingprojecta oceanmappingprojectb
sql: SELECT SUM(biomass) FROM SpeciesBiomass INNER JOIN OceanMappingProjects ON SpeciesBiomass.species = OceanMappingProjects.species WHERE OceanMappingProjects.project IN ('OceanMappingProjectA', 'OceanMappingProjectB');

sql_prompt: list underwater volcano arctic region depth greater 3000 meter
sql: SELECT name FROM underwater_volcanoes WHERE region = 'Arctic' AND depth > 3000;

sql_prompt: show number safety inspection per vessel mediterranean sea
sql: SELECT vessels.vessel_name, COUNT(safety_inspections.inspection_id) FROM vessels INNER JOIN safety_inspections ON vessels.vessel_id = safety_inspections.vessel_id WHERE vessels.region = 'Mediterranean' GROUP BY vessels.vessel_name;

sql_prompt: country source unsuccessful login attempt system s009 respective count
sql: SELECT login_country, COUNT(*) as count FROM unsuccessful_logins WHERE system_target = 'S009' GROUP BY login_country;

sql_prompt: list agricultural innovation project central america received funding world bank interamerican development bank
sql: SELECT project_name, location FROM AgriculturalInnovations WHERE funder IN ('World Bank', 'Inter-American Development Bank') AND location = 'Central America' GROUP BY project_name HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT funder) = 2;

sql_prompt: healthcare facility offer mental health service city
sql: SELECT DISTINCT Name FROM Facilities WHERE Location = 'City D' AND Services LIKE '%Mental Health%';

sql_prompt: many hour diversity inclusion training completed employee department
sql: SELECT SUM(Hours_Spent) FROM Training WHERE Employee_ID IN (SELECT Employee_ID FROM Employee WHERE Department = 'IT') AND Training_Type = 'Diversity and Inclusion';

sql_prompt: many yellow card given bayern munich player champion league
sql: SELECT SUM(cards) FROM yellow_cards JOIN games ON yellow_cards.team_id = games.team_id WHERE games.tournament = 'Champions League' AND yellow_cards.team_id = 1;

sql_prompt: basketball player ncaaplayers table taller 7 foot
sql: SELECT player_name FROM ncaa_players WHERE height > 96;

sql_prompt: average occupancy rate per hotel new york city ordered occupancy rate descending order
sql: SELECT AVG(occupancy_rate) AS avg_occupancy_rate, hotel_name FROM hotels WHERE city = 'New York City' GROUP BY hotel_name ORDER BY avg_occupancy_rate DESC;

sql_prompt: list organization 200 volunteer average donation amount excluding donation le 10
sql: SELECT o.org_name, AVG(donation_amount) AS avg_donation_amount FROM organizations o JOIN volunteers v ON o.org_id = v.org_id JOIN donations don ON o.org_id = don.org_id WHERE donation_amount >= 10 GROUP BY o.org_name HAVING COUNT(v.vol_id) > 200;

sql_prompt: total amount donated specific cause
sql: SELECT SUM(donation_amount) FROM donations JOIN causes ON donations.cause_id = causes.id WHERE causes.name = 'Cause A';

sql_prompt: total agricultural innovation output country southeast asia 2019
sql: SELECT country, SUM(innovation_output) FROM agri_innovation WHERE year = 2019 AND country IN ('Vietnam', 'Thailand', 'Indonesia') GROUP BY country;

sql_prompt: count job application received historically underrepresented community last 6 month
sql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM JobApplications WHERE ApplicantCommunity = 'Underrepresented' AND ApplicationDate >= DATEADD(month, -6, GETDATE());

sql_prompt: total number goal scored player soccerteams soccerplayergoals table team mascot starting letter c
sql: SELECT SUM(Goals) FROM SoccerPlayerGoals INNER JOIN SoccerTeams ON SoccerPlayerGoals.TeamID = SoccerTeams.TeamID WHERE Mascot LIKE 'C%';

sql_prompt: total number match played cricketmatches table match rained
sql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM CricketMatches WHERE Weather = 'Rain';

sql_prompt: many cultural heritage site japan spain
sql: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT country_id) FROM Cultural_Heritage_Sites WHERE country_id IN (1, 2);

sql_prompt: total revenue generated sustainable tourism activity indonesia
sql: SELECT SUM(revenue) FROM tourism_activities WHERE country = 'Indonesia' AND sustainable = TRUE;

sql_prompt: many whale spotted north atlantic summer month 2021
sql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM whale_sightings WHERE species = 'Blue Whale' OR species = 'Humpback Whale' AND location = 'North Atlantic' AND sighting_date BETWEEN '2021-06-01' AND '2021-08-31';

sql_prompt: top 5 common security incident financial sector last year
sql: SELECT incident_type, COUNT(*) as incident_count FROM incidents WHERE sector = 'Financial' GROUP BY incident_type ORDER BY incident_count DESC LIMIT 5;

sql_prompt: average claim amount policyholder car model corolla
sql: SELECT AVG(amount) FROM Claims INNER JOIN Auto ON Claims.policyholder_id = Auto.policyholder_id WHERE car_model = 'Corolla';

sql_prompt: policy term length policyholder highest risk assessment score
sql: SELECT policy_term_length FROM policies WHERE risk_assessment_score = (SELECT MAX(risk_assessment_score) FROM policies);

sql_prompt: average amount funding womenled agricultural innovation project nigeria partitioned year project funded
sql: SELECT AVG(FundingAmount) as AvgFunding, EXTRACT(YEAR FROM ProjectStartDate) as YearFromDate FROM AgriculturalInnovations WHERE ProjectLocation = 'Nigeria' AND LeaderGender = 'Female' GROUP BY YearFromDate;

sql_prompt: total number rural infrastructure project completed southeast asia 2018
sql: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT project) as total_projects FROM rural_infrastructure WHERE country IN ('Indonesia', 'Thailand', 'Philippines', 'Vietnam', 'Malaysia') AND year = 2018;

sql_prompt: many employee completed compliance training quarter
sql: SELECT QUARTER(completion_date) as completion_quarter, COUNT(*) as num_completed FROM training_records WHERE training_type = 'Compliance' AND completion_date IS NOT NULL GROUP BY completion_quarter;

sql_prompt: grand slam title tennis
sql: SELECT name FROM tennis_players WHERE grand_slam_titles = (SELECT MAX(grand_slam_titles) FROM tennis_players);

sql_prompt: average rating ecofriendly hotel france
sql: SELECT AVG(rating) FROM eco_hotels WHERE country = 'France';

sql_prompt: minimum depth recorded mariana trench
sql: SELECT MIN(depth) FROM ocean_floor_mapping WHERE location = 'Mariana Trench';

sql_prompt: average depth five deepest trench pacific ocean
sql: SELECT AVG(DEPTH) FROM (SELECT DEPTH FROM TRENCHES WHERE REGION = 'Pacific Ocean' ORDER BY DEPTH DESC LIMIT 5) AS T;

sql_prompt: total number threat indicator energy sector confidence level higher 75
sql: SELECT SUM(confidence) FROM threat_indicators WHERE sector = 'Energy' AND confidence > 75;

sql_prompt: list claim processed last 60 day
sql: SELECT ClaimID, ProcessingDate FROM Claims WHERE ProcessingDate >= DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE(), INTERVAL 60 DAY);
